<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạlmw̉mn ạlạ̉myn .. yfrḥ frḥ tẖmyn)2
 wạlkẖạṭy yẓl ḥzyn .. (lmạ yswʿ yyjy)3
 wạlkẖạṭy yẓl ḥzyn .. lmạ yyjy
 2- (yswʿ qạl ạ̉nạ jạy .. wạlmw̉mn ạkẖdh mʿạy)2
 tʿml yạ kẖạṭy ạ̹zạy .. (lmạ yswʿ yyjy)3
 tʿml yạ kẖạṭy ạzạy .. lmạ yyjy
 3- (yạ kẖạṭy twb wạrjʿ .. wlṣwt yswʿ ạsmʿ)2
 tndm wlạ ynfʿ .. (lmạ yswʿ yyjy)3
 tndm wlạ ynfʿ .. lmạ yyjy
 4- (lạ ynfʿk ạlmạl .. klạ wlạ ạljmạl)2
 ttgẖyr ạlạ̉ḥwạl .. (lmạ yswʿ yyjy)3
 ttgẖyr ạlạ̉ḥwạl .. lmạ yyjy
 5- (yswʿ ʿly ạlạ̉bwạb .. ạfrḥwạ yạ ạ̉ḥbạb)2
 snkẖṭf ʿly ạlsḥạb .. (lmạ yswʿ yyjy)3
 snkẖṭf ʿly̱ ạlsḥạb .. lmạ yyjy
 6- (sạʿẗ ʿsẖạ ạlkẖrwf .. njls ṣfwf ṣfwf)2
 bkrẗ ạlʿywn tsẖwf .. (lmạ yswʿ yyjy)3
 bkrẗ ạlʿywn tsẖwf .. lmạ yyjy</lyrics>
